

Video generation prompt
SEGMENT 1 — INTRO
Use this prompt:
Create an 8-second AI-generated video.
Voiceover: “AI isn’t just writing emails anymore. In 2025, it’s starting to act like a full-time employee. Here are five AI tools changing real jobs.”
Subtitles: “AI is becoming a full-time worker • 2025 is here • 5 tools changing jobs.”
Visual Style: Futuristic tech environment, glowing holograms, and  AI icons appearing around the screen. Show a digital human silhouette and animated circuits flowing behind them.
Camera Style: Slow zoom-in with gentle parallax motion.
On-Screen Text: “AI in 2025” and “5 Job-Replacing Tools”
Background: Dark blue + neon purple gradient with floating particles.
Music: Futuristic, upbeat tech music with soft synths.
Transitions: Fade-in from black, subtle warp transition at the end.

SEGMENT 2 — TOOL 1 INTRO
Prompt:
Create an 8-second video.
Voiceover: “Autonomous AI agents can plan tasks, research, write code, test projects, and manage entire workflows.”
Subtitles: “Autonomous AI agents can run full workflows on their own.”
Visual Style: Show an AI agent dashboard, automated tasks completing, glowing checkmarks, and code scrolling automatically.
Camera Style: Smooth left-to-right pan.
On-Screen Text: “AI Agents = Digital Employees.”
Background: Futuristic workspace with holographic UI.
Music: Steady tech beat.
Transitions: Slide-in UI elements.

